### Test Booking System
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@guestId = REPLACE_WITH_GUEST_ID
@bookingNumber = REPLACE_WITH_BOOKING_NUMBER

### 1. Create Guest First (prerequisite)
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "booking-test@example.com",
  "fullName": "Booking Test User",
  "phone": "+201234567890",
  "locale": "en"
}

### 2. Create Booking for TravelPack
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guestId": "{{guestId}}",
  "itemType": "travel_pack",
  "itemId": "REPLACE_WITH_TRAVEL_PACK_ID",
  "numberOfPersons": 2,
  "startDate": "2025-12-01T10:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-12-10T18:00:00Z",
  "locale": "en"
}

### 3. Create Booking for Activity
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guestId": "{{guestId}}",
  "itemType": "activity",
  "itemId": "REPLACE_WITH_ACTIVITY_ID",
  "numberOfPersons": 3,
  "locale": "en"
}

### 4. Create Booking for Car
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guestId": "{{guestId}}",
  "itemType": "car",
  "itemId": "REPLACE_WITH_CAR_ID",
  "numberOfDays": 7,
  "startDate": "2025-12-01T10:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-12-08T10:00:00Z",
  "locale": "en"
}

### 5. Get Booking by Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingNumber}}

### 6. Get All Bookings for Guest
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/guest/{{guestId}}

### 7. Update Booking Status (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingNumber}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### 8. Mark Booking as Paid
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingNumber}}/payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": "credit_card",
  "paymentTransactionId": "TXN-20251101-12345"
}

### 9. Cancel Booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingNumber}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Changed travel plans"
}

### 10. Get Booking Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/statistics

### 11. Get All Active Bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings

### 12. Cleanup Expired Bookings
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/cleanup-expired
